00:52:22,700 --> 00:52:23,820
 prošlo je par mjeseci,

1159
00:52:23,820 --> 00:52:25,080
 i,

1160
00:52:25,080 --> 00:52:26,820
 ustavno sam jedan san,

1161
00:52:26,820 --> 00:52:28,280
 neki divlji,

1162
00:52:28,280 --> 00:52:29,040
 da je svijet,

1163
00:52:29,040 --> 00:52:29,220
 ono,

1164
00:52:29,220 --> 00:52:29,880
 poludio,

1165
00:52:29,880 --> 00:52:30,820
 da jedne i druge,

1166
00:52:30,820 --> 00:52:31,400
 ono,

1167
00:52:31,400 --> 00:52:32,700
 ubijaju iz sporta,

1168
00:52:32,700 --> 00:52:33,820
 iz fore,

1169
00:52:33,920 --> 00:52:34,440
 izezancije,

1170
00:52:34,440 --> 00:52:36,400
 što se zapravo danas i događa na neki način,

1171
00:52:36,400 --> 00:52:38,740
 u svijetu možemo svašta vidjeti,

1172
00:52:38,740 --> 00:52:39,140
 ovoga,

1173
00:52:39,140 --> 00:52:39,940
 čega ima,

1174
00:52:39,940 --> 00:52:41,440
 ja sam skužao da jedna,

1175
00:52:41,440 --> 00:52:42,160
 moja,

1176
00:52:42,160 --> 00:52:43,760
 ono,

1177
00:52:43,760 --> 00:52:44,940
 jedan prijatelj,

1178
00:52:44,940 --> 00:52:46,180
 poznata osoba,

1179
00:52:46,180 --> 00:52:48,100
 da isto ima takav neki poriv,

1180
00:52:48,100 --> 00:52:49,520
 ja sam, ono,

1181
00:52:49,520 --> 00:52:51,060
 kao u tom snu,

1182
00:52:51,060 --> 00:52:53,060
 sam krenuo molit za nju,

1183
00:52:53,060 --> 00:52:53,480
 da, ono,

1184
00:52:53,480 --> 00:52:53,800
 daj,

1185
00:52:53,800 --> 00:52:54,520
 stani,

1186
00:52:54,520 --> 00:52:55,520
 ovoga,

1187
00:52:55,520 --> 00:52:56,640
 ne možeš ići dalje,

1188
00:52:56,640 --> 00:52:56,920
 ono,

1189
00:52:56,920 --> 00:52:57,820
 počinu sam molit,

1190
00:52:57,820 --> 00:52:58,580
 i,

1191
00:52:58,580 --> 00:53:00,800
 i toj osobi su se oči,

1192
00:53:00,800 --> 00:53:01,200
 ono,

1193
00:53:01,200 --> 00:53:02,700
 preokrenule,

1194
00:53:02,800 --> 00:53:03,660
 kao da je obsjednuta,

1195
00:53:03,660 --> 00:53:03,820
 ne,

1196
00:53:03,820 --> 00:53:05,860
 i u tom trenutku se san prekinuo,

1197
00:53:05,860 --> 00:53:06,360
 skroz,

1198
00:53:06,360 --> 00:53:07,940
 ja sam se onako probudio,

1199
00:53:07,940 --> 00:53:09,180
 a osno sam u nekoj,

1200
00:53:09,180 --> 00:53:09,840
 ono,

1201
00:53:09,840 --> 00:53:10,780
 nije san,

1202
00:53:10,780 --> 00:53:11,440
 ali nešto je,

1203
00:53:11,440 --> 00:53:12,180
 kao budno,

1204
00:53:12,180 --> 00:53:13,580
 nisam se mogao maknuti,

1205
00:53:13,580 --> 00:53:13,960
 nema sam,

1206
00:53:14,200 --> 00:53:15,320
 kraj sebe,

1207
00:53:15,320 --> 00:53:19,480
 osjetio prisutnost neke,

1208
00:53:19,480 --> 00:53:21,020
 neke osobe,

1209
00:53:21,020 --> 00:53:22,700
 neke spodobe,

1210
00:53:22,700 --> 00:53:24,220
 nisam mogao vidjeti,

1211
00:53:24,220 --> 00:53:24,880
 koja,

1212
00:53:24,880 --> 00:53:27,320
 me gleda,

1213
00:53:27,320 --> 00:53:29,860
 ne fizičkim očima,

1214
00:53:29,860 --> 00:53:31,200
 i reži na mene,

1215
00:53:31,200 --> 00:53:32,060
 reži na ako,

1216
00:53:32,060 --> 00:53:33,600
 u dubokim nekim frekvencijama,

1217
00:53:33,600 --> 00:53:35,680
 i ne može podnijeti,

1218
00:53:35,680 --> 00:53:36,800
 opće moje postojanje,

1219
00:53:36,920 --> 00:53:39,040
 mrzime i zna svog bića,

1220
00:53:39,040 --> 00:53:40,360
 tada mi je bilo jasno,

1221
00:53:40,360 --> 00:53:41,480
 da tako čovjek ne može,

1222
00:53:41,480 --> 00:53:42,920
 nijedan čovjek tako ne može mrzit,

1223
00:53:42,920 --> 00:53:45,460
 da to nije nekakva ljudska osoba,

1224
00:53:45,460 --> 00:53:46,380
 nego da je to,

1225
00:53:46,380 --> 00:53:47,340
 vjerojatno,

1226
00:53:47,340 --> 00:53:47,780
 zloduh.

1227
00:53:47,780 --> 00:53:48,920
 Ja sam,

1228
00:53:48,920 --> 00:53:50,420
 u tom trenutku nisam mogao pomaknuti,

1229
00:53:50,420 --> 00:53:50,900
 ni ruke,

1230
00:53:50,900 --> 00:53:51,400
 ni noge,

1231
00:53:51,400 --> 00:53:51,840
 ništa,

1232
00:53:51,840 --> 00:53:52,500
 samo onako,

1233
00:53:52,500 --> 00:53:53,540
 ostav sam paraliziran,

1234
00:53:53,540 --> 00:53:55,120
 jedino što sam mogao,

1235
00:53:55,120 --> 00:53:56,600
 u dubini srca,

1236
00:53:56,600 --> 00:53:56,980
 duše,

1237
00:53:56,980 --> 00:53:58,160
 izreći Isuse,

1238
00:53:58,160 --> 00:53:59,360
 kako sam prvi put rekao,

1239
00:53:59,360 --> 00:54:00,500
 izrekao Isuse,

1240
00:54:00,500 --> 00:54:02,160
 tako je to malo popustilo,

1241
00:54:02,280 --> 00:54:03,540
 pa onda još Isuse,

1242
00:54:03,540 --> 00:54:04,440
 još je popustilo,

1243
00:54:04,440 --> 00:54:04,940
 pa još,

1244
00:54:04,940 --> 00:54:05,260
 još,

1245
00:54:05,260 --> 00:54:07,880
 dok nisam na usta uspio izreći Isuse

1246
00:54:07,880 --> 00:54:09,720
 i tad je to otišlo od mene skroz.

1247
00:54:09,720 --> 00:54:10,960
 A tad sam se baš uplašio,

1248
00:54:10,960 --> 00:54:11,520
 ono kao,

1249
00:54:11,520 --> 00:54:13,640
 kao mali klinac koji se boji

1250
00:54:13,640 --> 00:54:14,740
 nekog čudovišta mraka

1251
00:54:14,740 --> 00:54:15,600
 na toj razini.

1252
00:54:15,600 --> 00:54:17,140
 A nisam se bojao ničega,

1253
00:54:17,140 --> 00:54:18,240
 tad sam znao i po šumi,

1254
00:54:18,240 --> 00:54:18,640
 ono,

1255
00:54:18,640 --> 00:54:20,600
 kao trenirat rano i jutro,

1256
00:54:20,600 --> 00:54:21,740
 još za mraka,

1257
00:54:21,740 --> 00:54:22,820
 ono, trčati tako da,

1258
00:54:22,820 --> 00:54:24,360
 ja uopće nimi je bilo strah ničega.

1259
00:54:24,360 --> 00:54:26,140
 A ovdje sam se toliko uplašio,

1260
00:54:27,160 --> 00:54:28,560
 da mi sad neko dođe,

1261
00:54:28,560 --> 00:54:29,940
 sam puta puta to rekao,

1262
00:54:29,940 --> 00:54:31,140
 da mi neko dođe s pištoljem,

1263
00:54:31,140 --> 00:54:33,260
 ne bi bio takav strah

1264
00:54:33,260 --> 00:54:34,800
 kao kad sam to osjetio.

1265
00:54:34,800 --> 00:54:36,980
 I osjetio sam stvarnu prisutnost zla

1266
00:54:36,980 --> 00:54:39,400
 i da je stvarna borba za moj život

1267
00:54:39,400 --> 00:54:40,800
 i da nije to šala neka.

1268
00:54:40,800 --> 00:54:43,120
 Da ja mogu opet sad malo se zezati ovo,

1269
00:54:43,120 --> 00:54:45,020
 ono, da je stvarno borba za nas sve,

1270
00:54:45,020 --> 00:54:48,060
 ono, na život i smrt zapravo.

1271
00:54:48,060 --> 00:54:55,140
 Evo ga, tu bi.

1272
00:54:57,160 --> 00:55:02,220
 I tako se moj muž vratio

1273
00:55:02,220 --> 00:55:04,460
 gospodinu, meni i obitelji

1274
00:55:04,460 --> 00:55:06,600
 i dobila sam još bolji model,

1275
00:55:06,600 --> 00:55:09,940
 još napredniji model.

1276
00:55:09,940 --> 00:55:11,940
 I, i, i...

1277
00:55:11,940 --> 00:55:15,020
 Evo, gospodin me baš

1278
00:55:15,020 --> 00:55:19,920
 nagradio, obdario

1279
00:55:19,920 --> 00:55:21,600
 takvim mužem.

1280
00:55:21,600 --> 00:55:24,040
 On je,

1281
00:55:24,960 --> 00:55:27,440
 naši djevojčice su tada bile,

1282
00:55:27,440 --> 00:55:29,420
 oni su vidjeli tatu

1283
00:55:29,420 --> 00:55:31,280
 kako je živio prije.

1284
00:55:31,280 --> 00:55:31,660
 Znači,

1285
00:55:31,660 --> 00:55:33,900
 znači, on je najdeblje cigare

1286
00:55:33,900 --> 00:55:34,840
 koje postaje,

1287
00:55:34,840 --> 00:55:35,720
 on je to pušio,

1288
00:55:35,720 --> 00:55:37,760
 on je sve što ide uz to

1289
00:55:37,760 --> 00:55:38,600
 činio.

1290
00:55:38,600 --> 00:55:39,760
 I one su njega doživjeli

1291
00:55:39,760 --> 00:55:40,640
 u tom stanju

1292
00:55:40,640 --> 00:55:41,960
 i onda su ga i doživjeli

1293
00:55:41,960 --> 00:55:42,800
 kada se tata

1294
00:55:42,800 --> 00:55:44,220
 obratio.

1295
00:55:44,220 --> 00:55:46,040
 I neizmjerno sam

1296
00:55:46,040 --> 00:55:47,380
 zahvalna gospodinu

1297
00:55:47,380 --> 00:55:48,220
 na tom drugom

1298
00:55:48,220 --> 00:55:50,180
 obraćenju Lukinom

1299
00:55:50,180 --> 00:55:55,580
 i uvijek se

1300
00:55:55,580 --> 00:55:57,720
 hvalim njime.

1301
00:55:57,720 --> 00:56:00,960
 Neki dan,

1302
00:56:00,960 --> 00:56:02,800
 mi baš prijatelji su mu i rekli

1303
00:56:02,800 --> 00:56:05,440
 pa ti se zapravo hvališ

1304
00:56:05,440 --> 00:56:06,220
 sa svojim mužem.

1305
00:56:06,320 --> 00:56:07,200
 kažem, da,

1306
00:56:07,200 --> 00:56:11,440
 još ću ne mislim prestati.

1307
00:56:11,440 --> 00:56:16,260
 I gospodin je obnovio

1308
00:56:16,260 --> 00:56:18,340
 našu zajedničku molitvu,

1309
00:56:18,340 --> 00:56:20,240
 ono, kada smo nas dvoje,

1310
00:56:20,240 --> 00:56:20,840
 nas samo,

1311
00:56:20,840 --> 00:56:22,600
 našu obiteljsku molitvu,

1312
00:56:22,600 --> 00:56:25,840
 da konačno sa djecom

1313
00:56:25,840 --> 00:56:27,480
 počnemo moliti,

1314
00:56:27,480 --> 00:56:28,860
 jer bilo kakva molitva

1315
00:56:28,860 --> 00:56:31,260
 i bilo kakva duhovna pjesma

1316
00:56:31,260 --> 00:56:34,000
 je bila zabranjena

1317
00:56:34,000 --> 00:56:37,580
 u ovom teškom razdoblju.

1318
00:56:37,580 --> 00:56:43,160
 I tu mi je gospodin pokazivao

1319
00:56:43,160 --> 00:56:47,020
 što je muškarac u braku

1320
00:56:47,020 --> 00:56:48,540
 i što je žena u braku,

1321
00:56:48,540 --> 00:56:52,320
 prepuštanje njegovom vodstvu

1322
00:56:52,320 --> 00:56:58,020
 i prihvaćanju moje drugotnosti

1323
00:56:58,020 --> 00:57:01,500
 i podlaganju svome mužu,

1324
00:57:01,500 --> 00:57:03,640
 jer društvo nam govori drugačije.

1325
00:57:04,000 --> 00:57:07,640
 Evo, u tom obračenju,

1326
00:57:07,640 --> 00:57:09,580
 u tom zanosu koji mi se dogodio

1327
00:57:09,580 --> 00:57:10,480
 to jutro sam,

1328
00:57:10,480 --> 00:57:12,300
 kak sam bio na tim koljenima,

1329
00:57:12,300 --> 00:57:14,200
 sam molio isto nekakve molite

1330
00:57:14,200 --> 00:57:15,880
 koje nisam planirao moliti.

1331
00:57:15,880 --> 00:57:19,400
 I jedna od tih molitava je bila,

1332
00:57:19,400 --> 00:57:22,260
 ono, Bože, ti ovu kuću,

1333
00:57:22,260 --> 00:57:22,800
 ovaj stan,

1334
00:57:22,800 --> 00:57:24,560
 čini kućom molitve,

1335
00:57:24,560 --> 00:57:26,120
 domom molitve.

1336
00:57:27,160 --> 00:57:28,960
 i stvarno za pola godine su došli

1337
00:57:28,960 --> 00:57:31,880
 prvi molitelji kod nas,

1338
00:57:31,880 --> 00:57:34,380
 jedna grupa, jedna ekipa

1339
00:57:34,380 --> 00:57:35,820
 od koje smo prije znali,

1340
00:57:35,820 --> 00:57:36,940
 zajedno su s nama molili,

1341
00:57:36,940 --> 00:57:37,960
 bili su u toj zajednici,

1342
00:57:37,960 --> 00:57:40,180
 su trebali neku potrebu

1343
00:57:40,180 --> 00:57:41,200
 da se nešto pomolimo.

1344
00:57:42,800 --> 00:57:43,520
 nek dođu,

1345
00:57:43,520 --> 00:57:44,480
 gađen Dubraki dođu,

1346
00:57:44,480 --> 00:57:46,100
 nek dođu pa ćemo moliti zajedno.

1347
00:57:46,100 --> 00:57:48,840
 A oni su čuli da sam se ja okrenuo,

1348
00:57:48,840 --> 00:57:49,520
 obratio,

1349
00:57:49,520 --> 00:57:51,120
 pa su rekli,

1350
00:57:51,120 --> 00:57:51,860
 pa zar i on?

1351
00:57:51,860 --> 00:57:53,340
 Očito je u to vrijeme

1352
00:57:53,340 --> 00:57:55,340
 gospodin radio na mnogima,

1353
00:57:55,340 --> 00:57:57,360
 radio jedan zahvat po Hrvatskoj

1354
00:57:57,360 --> 00:57:58,340
 za mlade,

1355
00:57:58,340 --> 00:57:59,500
 po mladima,

1356
00:57:59,500 --> 00:58:02,600
 vuko ih je nazad u crkvu,

1357
00:58:02,600 --> 00:58:04,340
 tad su naštali Božja pobjeda

1358
00:58:04,340 --> 00:58:05,420
 i mnoge druge zajednice.

1359
00:58:05,420 --> 00:58:07,740
 I tako su, ono,

1360
00:58:07,740 --> 00:58:10,100
 došli su molitelji kod nas doma

1361
00:58:10,100 --> 00:58:12,300
 i tu smo startali

1362
00:58:12,300 --> 00:58:14,940
 kroz neko kratko vrijeme

1363
00:58:14,940 --> 00:58:16,340
 kućnu molitvenu grupu

1364
00:58:16,340 --> 00:58:18,240
 koja je rasla sve više i više

1365
00:58:18,240 --> 00:58:20,940
 i koja je prerasla zapravo

1366
00:58:20,940 --> 00:58:22,540
 u molitvenu zajednicu

1367
00:58:22,540 --> 00:58:25,040
 koja se dobila naziv

1368
00:58:25,040 --> 00:58:25,940
 Sluge beskorisne

1369
00:58:25,940 --> 00:58:27,180
 jer mi bez gospodina

1370
00:58:27,180 --> 00:58:28,380
 ne možemo ništa učiniti.

1371
00:58:28,380 --> 00:58:29,180
 Za to smo vidili,

1372
00:58:29,180 --> 00:58:30,480
 kroz sve ove korake

1373
00:58:30,480 --> 00:58:32,660
 bez njega sam niko i ništa.

1374
00:58:32,660 --> 00:58:34,860
 I onda smo,

1375
00:58:34,860 --> 00:58:35,780
 evo, kao zajednice

1376
00:58:35,780 --> 00:58:36,580
 smo se prijavili

1377
00:58:36,580 --> 00:58:39,600
 u KKODS,

1378
00:58:39,600 --> 00:58:40,880
 Katoličku kvalitvensku odboru

1379
00:58:40,880 --> 00:58:41,620
 u duhu svetom,

1380
00:58:41,800 --> 00:58:43,060
 krenula su, ono,

1381
00:58:43,060 --> 00:58:44,000
 mnoga služenja,

1382
00:58:44,000 --> 00:58:46,400
 slavljenja,

1383
00:58:46,400 --> 00:58:47,460
 molitve za druge,

1384
00:58:47,460 --> 00:58:48,500
 prošli smo nekakve

1385
00:58:48,500 --> 00:58:49,780
 edukacijano unbounda,

1386
00:58:49,780 --> 00:58:51,760
 počeli smo moliti unbound

1387
00:58:51,760 --> 00:58:55,380
 i baš se služenje

1388
00:58:55,380 --> 00:58:56,600
 sve više se umnažalo

1389
00:58:56,600 --> 00:58:57,440
 i tako dalje.

1390
00:58:58,720 --> 00:58:59,720
 Međutim, evo,

1391
00:58:59,720 --> 00:59:01,340
 sad je sve super,

1392
00:59:01,340 --> 00:59:02,900
 zajedno smo,

1393
00:59:02,900 --> 00:59:05,220
 molimo zajedno,

1394
00:59:05,220 --> 00:59:07,840
 međutim,

1395
00:59:07,840 --> 00:59:09,460
 se meni opet dogodilo nekakva,

1396
00:59:09,460 --> 00:59:10,960
 nije pad,

1397
00:59:10,960 --> 00:59:12,840
 ali nekakva pretjeranost

1398
00:59:12,840 --> 00:59:13,800
 u tom služenju,

1399
00:59:13,800 --> 00:59:14,780
 gdje sam opet pobrko

1400
00:59:14,780 --> 00:59:16,580
 nekakve prioritete.

1401
00:59:17,380 --> 00:59:17,760
 ovo ga,

1402
00:59:17,760 --> 00:59:18,960
 to,

1403
00:59:18,960 --> 00:59:20,440
 možda,

1404
00:59:20,440 --> 00:59:21,680
 pretjerano služenje

1405
00:59:21,680 --> 00:59:22,580
 mi je uzelo

1406
00:59:22,580 --> 00:59:24,860
 prvo odnos s Bogom,

1407
00:59:24,860 --> 00:59:26,540
 ja sam molio za druge,

1408
00:59:26,540 --> 00:59:28,200
 molio sam svašta,

1409
00:59:28,200 --> 00:59:29,300
 slavio i tako dalje,

1410
00:59:29,300 --> 00:59:30,460
 ali temeljni odnos s Bogom

1411
00:59:30,460 --> 00:59:31,460
 sam onako zanemario

1412
00:59:31,460 --> 00:59:33,480
 i zanemaljio sam odnos

1413
00:59:33,480 --> 00:59:34,800
 s Dubravkom.

1414
00:59:34,800 --> 00:59:39,680
 Nekako sam,

1415
00:59:39,680 --> 00:59:41,000
 počeo sam je,

1416
00:59:41,000 --> 00:59:42,780
 ako bi ona rekla,

1417
00:59:42,780 --> 00:59:44,660
 svačao sam je predoslovno.

1418
00:59:44,660 --> 00:59:45,860
 Nisam opet,

1419
